{"tid":1598264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於香港獨立一事","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T12:51:01.000Z","uid":205482,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2f7e316fff89ed64bcfcd4bfa5ef8ac404f29a96","tid":1598264,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:02:02.000Z","msg":"利申:借ac<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭喺對話已經講咗一國兩制&ne;香港自治<br />\n依個喺核彈黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n代表林鄭以一國兩制之名反對香港自治<br />\n違背基本法賦予嘅港人治港,高度自治<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>證明一國兩制及基本法不能給予香港人高度自治    </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n美國都比咗好多tips我地<br />\n依家手足玩火魔法 美國都可以當睇唔到 繼續指責中共同香港警察<br />\n依家可能喺宣揚香港獨立嘅最佳時機<br />\n我地要寫明 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立宣言</span></strong><br />\n指明中共以一國兩制嘅大話去剝奪香港人自治及自由<br />\n絕對需要講清楚比世界聽<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港獨立是被逼出來的<br />\nThe last way for us to have freedom and democracy is independent<br />\nWe don't want, but CCP make all this.</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭話一國兩制&ne;香港自治 絕對喺核彈</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"455cf419bf8fe98e5de0428557863cb90a55aa1a","tid":1598264,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"光復"},{"pid":"e68990b85da8444ebc0b0e96864e79b1a08bf678","tid":1598264,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"455cf419bf8fe98e5de0428557863cb90a55aa1a","tid":1598264,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:02:20.000Z","msg":"光復"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:02:30.000Z","msg":"香港"},{"pid":"6ed2b649d6e99f60ed880481150edde815f486b2","tid":1598264,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:02:40.000Z","msg":"時代"},{"pid":"966d914b926545fbf64186367cc6ff93df60dc80","tid":1598264,"uid":183734,"li