 /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWfr1E9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWfr1E9.jpg&h=defd0334&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdP4Oj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdP4Oj9.jpg&h=386586b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7oECdw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7oECdw.jpg&h=958bedcb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NXBVU0d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNXBVU0d.jpg&h=e5ebef22&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b1df4940de29e27be0e58fa3fddfa5586abd288","tid":1598264,"uid":111934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:09:35.000Z","msg":"經歷咗廿二年中共統治<br />\n一早已經有哂高舉獨立大旗嘅大義名份<br />\n只係好多人一係大中華膠<br />\n一係私心作崇, 想延續失敗抗爭, 入建制撈一筆<br />\n一係就真心驚中共, 怕會遇到強力鎮壓<br />\n再唔係就係自家有後路, 知道就算香港無民主都可以獨善其身"},{"pid":"d50cadf33fbadfba98c31e1ecd0a85f896866aec","tid":1598264,"uid":45991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全民反DQ 一個不能少</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1596375/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1596375/page/1</a><br />\n不如就喺十月一土共生日，香港人不分和理勇、不分界別、不分範籌，一次過請哂所界別既人上去民間記者會同佢做生日</span>"},{"pid":"ce3f9db7da325f36975f5c2e58e5b4ee2315dbaf","tid":1598264,"uid":301989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:12:39.000Z","msg":"樓主好快會畀時機撚屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf7f96c150d0ac8ed65c539f88e9abea693753b","tid":1598264,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港獨立就係唯一出路</span>"},{"pid":"24d8c30cc2de2c1c4a34a5cec783798314f6dce5","tid":1598264,"uid":314509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"966d914b926545fbf64186367c